    About this product

    Tread in standout style with this unisex black laptop backpack from the Joshua collection by Tommy Hilfiger. Designed to suit the preference of urban people, it exudes a textured pattern. It also comes with adjustable straps and a zip closure to ensure the safety of your valuables. Made of high-quality polyester, this backpack will certainly last long. To accommodate a 15-inch laptop and other essentials in a safe manner, this backpack comprises 3 compartments.
